title: Iano Imbeni
text:
Iano Simão da Silva Imbeni (born 2 February 1999) is a <a href="Guinea-Bissau">Bissau-Guinean</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for Spanish club <a href="Deportivo%20Fabril">Deportivo Fabril</a>.
International career.
He made his debut for <a href="Guinea-Bissau%20national%20football%20team">Guinea-Bissau national football team</a> on 15 November 2021 in a <a href="2022%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20qualification%20%E2%80%93%20CAF%20Second%20Round">World Cup qualifier</a> against <a href="Sudan%20national%20football%20team">Sudan</a>.
